Package player

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • player.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.util.Observer

    public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.util.Observer, java.io.Serializable
    This class is the brains of the application. It handles the connection between player and server. As well as it decides the order in which order the methods in the Battleship class are called. for the player's connection. It implements the Observer interface and observes InputLitener class' updates.
    Author:
    DigitalVilla
